This folder will have the scripts for training and application of different algorithms provided by 
Toolkit for Multivariate Data Analysis (TMVA) with ROOT.

Now we only have the 

The input files are in ../Preselection/NTuples but they are just test files. 

How to run (root include in basf2),
    root -l ./TMVAClassification.C\(\"BDT\"\)
where we used BDT algorithm but the default algorithms will be trained without arguments.

TMVAClassification.C is just for training, the script for application to a different sample is required.
